{"tid":2154941,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好憎蔥、韮菜同洋蔥果啲","createTime":"2020-08-13T12:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T16:43:38.000Z","uid":363886,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fb85b85114268cc01c203827191191c9c4b3895c","tid":2154941,"uid":363886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"聞到已經作嘔，咬到嘅話真係黃膽水都嘔埋岀嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有蒜只可以食蒜茸，一大舊咬到又係嘔。<br />\n唔食蔥真係好多嘢都食得唔方便，杯麵餃子菜肉包小籠包<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岀面食西餐好多會切到洋蔥好碎，食到少少又即嘔，好冇癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed72b0fdd445e27bc8f43fd6978f2a5b5626e7d","tid":2154941,"uid":312363,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"只憎炎西"},{"pid":"91d7968da86312931cc65f5975f5c9946fc51495","tid":2154941,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65102b7506c645e050c3242c27137855c123e2ff","tid":2154941,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"你講嗰啲都係我最愛<br />\n就算碟邊嗰少少我都唔會放過"},{"pid":"b524924e8102bf74cb4e8f85fa9b987189f648e7","tid":2154941,"uid":363886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed72b0fdd445e27bc8f43fd6978f2a5b5626e7d","tid":2154941,"uid":312363,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"只憎炎西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"茜我唔會食佢，但聞到冇嘢。<br />\n蔥真係遠遠聞到已經反曬胃"},{"pid":"5e59fef7b28137ba3351e73969d1bff9a626fc3a","tid":2154941,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc94964f523f509094f9afee34d9136